UI card design spec (comprehensive)

=== CARD STRUCTURE ===
Overall: Minimal, no heavy shadows. rounded-xl, border (1px), shadow-none.
Always use: `shadow-none pt-0 rounded-xl` on Card component.
Card padding removed from top (pt-0) to allow header to sit flush with rounded corners.

Header (CardHeader):
- Tinted background with matching border color.
- Class pattern: `bg-{color}-50 border-{color}-{shade} border-b rounded-t-xl pt-6`
- No top padding on card itself; header has pt-6 for internal spacing.
- Border on bottom of header separates from content (border-b).
- Header sits flush with card's rounded corners (rounded-t-xl).

Title & Description:
- Title: `text-base` (or `text-sm sm:text-base` for responsive), status-tinted text color.
- Description: `text-xs`, slightly muted status color, optional font-mono for code-like text.
- Grid layout for header content: `grid grid-cols-[auto_minmax(0,1fr)_auto] gap-3 sm:gap-4`
- Icon: `h-5 w-5 mt-0.5` aligned left, uses same status color.
- Title/description can be wrapped in Tooltip for truncation handling with `cursor-help`.

Content (CardContent):
- Clean white background (default).
- Standard spacing: `px-6 py-4` inside content.
- Inputs/buttons use neutral styling; only status-specific elements get color.
- Can have nested components like Tabs, Accordion, etc.

=== STATUS COLOR SCHEMES ===
Connection Status:
- green: Connected (border-green-300, bg-green-50, text-green-900)
- amber: Connecting/Warning (border-amber-300, bg-amber-50, text-amber-900)
- red: Error (border-red-300, bg-red-50, text-red-900)
- gray: Default/Disconnected (border-gray-200, bg-gray-50, text-gray-900)

Topic Card Status (multi-state):
- green: Subscribed (border-green-300, bg-green-50, text-green-900)
- purple: Publishing (border-purple-300, bg-purple-50, text-purple-900)
- amber: Inactive (border-amber-200, bg-amber-50, text-amber-900)
- Mixed states use gradient or neutral colors

Graph Visualizations:
- teal: RQT Graph (border-teal-200, bg-teal-50, text-teal-900/800)
- purple: Details Panel (border-purple-200, bg-purple-50, text-purple-900)

=== BADGES & STATE INDICATORS ===
Pattern: Badge positioned on right side of header or inline.
Status Badge Structure:
- Container: `bg-{color}-100 text-{color}-700 hover:bg-{color}-100 border-{color}-200`
- Size: `text-xs` for compact badges
- Animated indicators: `h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-{color}-500 animate-pulse` for active states
- Icon badges: Use `h-3 w-3` icons with `animate-spin` for loading states
- Layout: Flex with gap-1.5 for icon + text

Badge Variants:
- Status badge: Color-matched with pulse indicator
- Outline badge: `variant="outline"` for secondary information
- Topic type badges: Publisher (purple), Subscriber (green), System (gray)

=== BUTTONS ===
Primary Actions:
- Default: `bg-gray-200 border-gray-500 border-1 text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-300 hover:text-gray-700`
- Status-specific: `bg-{color}-200 border-{color}-500 border-1 hover:bg-{color}-500 hover:text-white text-{color}-500`
- Example: Subscribe (green), Publish (purple)

Destructive Actions:
- Pattern: `variant="outline" border-red-{shade} text-red-600 hover:bg-red-50 hover:text-red-700`
- Used for: Unsubscribe, Disconnect, Stop actions

Loading States:
- Use `Loader2` icon with `animate-spin`
- Disable button during loading
- Keep label concise: "Connecting...", "Loading..."

Icon Buttons:
- Size: `size="sm"` or `h-4 w-4` icons
- Ghost variant for secondary actions
- Tooltips recommended for icon-only buttons

=== TABS ===
Container: Tabs component inside CardContent.
TabsList: `grid w-full grid-cols-{count}` for equal-width tabs.
TabsTrigger:
- Size: `text-xs` for compact interfaces
- Icons: `h-3 w-3 mr-1` before text
- Commonly used icons: Radio (info), Eye (subscribe), Send (publish)

TabsContent:
- Margin: `mt-4` from tabs list
- Contains tab-specific components

=== ACCORDION & COLLAPSIBLE ===
AccordionItem:
- Trigger: `text-sm hover:no-underline`
- Icon + text layout in trigger
- Icons: FileCode, Users, BarChart3, etc. (`h-4 w-4 text-gray-600`)

AccordionContent:
- Spacing: `space-y-2` or `space-y-3` for content sections
- Code blocks: `bg-gray-50 border rounded-lg p-3` with `font-mono text-xs`
- Empty states: `border-2 border-dashed rounded-lg p-3` or `p-4` with centered text

Collapsible:
- Button trigger with chevron icons (ChevronDown/ChevronRight)
- CollapsibleContent with `mt-2` spacing

=== INPUTS & FORMS ===
Input:
- Background: `bg-white` for contrast
- Standard styling with focus states
- Disabled when connection active or operation in progress

Textarea:
- Pattern: `w-full min-h-[200px] p-3 font-mono text-sm border rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-{color}-500 bg-white`
- Used for JSON editing in publish tabs
- Error states: Red border and error message below

Label:
- Pattern: `text-sm font-medium`
- Optional tooltip icon (`Info h-3.5 w-3.5`) for help text
- Help text: `text-xs text-gray-500` below input

Switch:
- Pattern: `data-[state=checked]:bg-indigo-500` or status color
- Layout: `flex items-center justify-between` with label + switch

=== TOOLTIPS ===
TooltipProvider wraps interactive elements.
Pattern:
- TooltipTrigger: `asChild` prop for wrapping other elements
- TooltipContent: `max-w-xs` or `max-w-sm`, `colorVariant={statusColor}`
- Used for: Truncated text (topic names, types), Icon buttons, Info icons
- Icons: `Info h-3.5 w-3.5 text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 cursor-help`

=== EMPTY STATES ===
Container: `bg-gray-50 border-2 border-dashed border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8 max-w-md text-center`
Icon: Large icon (h-12 w-12) with muted color (text-gray-400)
Text:
- Title: `text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2`
- Description: `text-sm text-gray-500`

Loading States:
- Pattern: Card with `bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6 max-w-md`
- Icon + message + SpinnerCustom component
- Action button linking to settings/connection page

=== PAGE LAYOUT ===
Container: `w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto py-8` (or max-w-4xl for narrower pages)
Header Section:
- Title: `text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight`
- Description: `text-muted-foreground mt-2`
- Spacing: `mb-8` before content

Content Grid:
- Topics/Services: `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4`
- Single column: Standard flow

=== GRAPH VISUALIZATIONS ===
Controls Card:
- Pattern: Teal theme (`border-teal-200`, `bg-teal-50`, `text-teal-900`)
- Compact layout with badges, search, filter buttons
- Collapsible filters section with `border-t border-gray-200`

Main Graph Card:
- Same teal theme as controls
- ReactFlow embedded in CardContent with specific height
- Fullscreen support with conditional styling

Details Panel:
- Purple theme (`border-purple-200`, `bg-purple-50`, `text-purple-900`)
- Collapsible with chevron icon in header
- Scrollable content sections with `max-h-48 overflow-y-auto`
- Copy buttons for data export

Graph Nodes:
- Nodes: Rectangular with colored border, white background
- Topics: Circular (rounded-full) with amber theme
- Selected state: `ring-2 ring-{color}-500 ring-offset-2`

=== DATA DISPLAY ===
Key-Value Pairs:
- Layout: `flex justify-between items-start gap-3 py-2 border-b`
- Label: `text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 flex-shrink-0`
- Value: `text-sm font-mono text-gray-900 text-right break-all`

Code Blocks:
- Container: `bg-gray-50 border rounded-lg p-3`
- Content: `text-xs font-mono text-gray-800 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words overflow-x-auto`

Lists with Badges:
- Layout: `flex flex-wrap gap-2`
- Badge pattern: `bg-{color}-50 text-{color}-700 border-{color}-200 text-xs`
- Empty state: Dashed border container with centered message

=== SEPARATORS ===
Pattern: `<Separator />` component between form sections
Spacing: Usually between major form groups (spacing: `space-y-6` in container)

=== ADVANCED SECTIONS ===
Pattern: Bordered container with title
- Container: `p-4 rounded-lg border`
- Title: `text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900 flex items-center gap-2`
- Icon: `h-4 w-4`
- Content: Standard form layout inside

=== ACCESSIBILITY ===
- Sufficient contrast for tinted headers (test with status colors)
- Clear focus styles on interactive elements
- Tooltips for truncated content and icon-only buttons
- ARIA labels where appropriate
- Keyboard navigation support for all interactive elements

=== RESPONSIVE DESIGN ===
- Text sizes: `text-sm sm:text-base` for responsive scaling
- Grid layouts: `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3`
- Gap spacing: `gap-3 sm:gap-4` for responsive spacing
- Badge text: Hidden on mobile with `hidden sm:inline` / `sm:hidden` for compact view
